{
 "_meta": {
  "npc": "Fyodor",
  "role": "彩衣織匠，手指修長靈巧；織機設計來自不列顛王舊書。會提到 L. Frank Baum 的『奧茲巫師』與新馬精西亞織絲師夏綠蒂（Charlotte）。為玩家熱氣球線索鋪墊。"
 },
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 2,
   "len": 6,
   "en": "Fyodor",
   "zh": "費歐多",
   "zh_bytes": 6,
   "note": "人名音譯；len=6 容三字"
  },
  {
   "offset": 10,
   "len": 66,
   "en": "a man in a multicolored jacket. His fingers are long and graceful.",
   "zh": "一名身披彩衣之人，手指修長而靈巧。",
   "zh_bytes": 34,
   "note": "描述句"
  },
  {
   "offset": 85,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Hello again, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「$G，又見面了。」",
   "zh_bytes": 18,
   "note": "保留 $G"
  },
  {
   "offset": 104,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Good $T, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「$T好，$G。」",
   "zh_bytes": 14,
   "note": "緊；保留 $T/$G"
  },
  {
   "offset": 129,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"What can I do for you?\"",
   "zh": "「我能為汝效何勞？」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 156,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "name",
   "zh": "名字",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "@name keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 161,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"My name is Fyodor. What is thy name?\"",
   "zh": "「我喚作費歐多。汝姓甚名誰？」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 202,
   "len": 28,
   "en": "\"Pleased to meet thee, `$Z.\"",
   "zh": "「幸會，`$Z。」",
   "zh_bytes": 15,
   "note": "保留 `$Z 變數（玩家輸入名字）"
  },
  {
   "offset": 242,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "job",
   "zh": "業",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "@job keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 246,
   "len": 62,
   "en": "\"I make cloth upon my @loom. Perhaps you'd like to @buy some.\"",
   "zh": "「我以@loom（織機）織布。汝或想@buy（買）。」",
   "zh_bytes": 32,
   "note": "@loom → @織機；@buy → @買"
  },
  {
   "offset": 314,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "buy",
   "zh": "買",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "@buy keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 331,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"I fear I have none with me, $G.\"",
   "zh": "「恐怕我此處無存貨，$G。」",
   "zh_bytes": 26,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 367,
   "len": 53,
   "en": "\"Come back when I'm at my loom; I'll help thee then.\"",
   "zh": "「待我在織機前時再來，我便為汝服務。」",
   "zh_bytes": 38,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 427,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "sell",
   "zh": "賣",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "@sell keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 445,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"But I don't need wool here, $G!\"",
   "zh": "「但我此地用不上羊毛，$G！」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 481,
   "len": 58,
   "en": "\"Come back when I'm at my loom; I'll deal with thee then.\"",
   "zh": "「待我在織機前時再來，我便與汝交易。」",
   "zh_bytes": 38,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 546,
   "len": 9,
   "en": "clot,loom",
   "zh": "布,織機",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "keyword 群組"
  },
  {
   "offset": 563,
   "len": 44,
   "en": "\"I push the pedals with my feet--like this.\"",
   "zh": "「以足踩動踏板——像這樣。」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 610,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"Then I pull these levers.\"",
   "zh": "「然後拉動這些把手。」",
   "zh_bytes": 22,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 640,
   "len": 72,
   "en": "\"The pattern depends on which combinations of levers and pedals I move.\"",
   "zh": "「花紋取決於我移動把手與踏板的各種組合。」",
   "zh_bytes": 42,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 715,
   "len": 106,
   "en": "\"My father's loom was not so complicated as mine. This design came from one of Lord British's old @books.\"",
   "zh": "「家父之織機不若此般繁複。此設計來自不列顛王一本舊@books（書）。」",
   "zh_bytes": 57,
   "note": "Lord British → 不列顛王（首次出現用全稱）"
  },
  {
   "offset": 827,
   "len": 94,
   "en": "\"I work on a large new loom. The plans for it were found in one of Lord British's old @books.\"",
   "zh": "「我所操作之新織機甚大。圖樣來自不列顛王一本舊@books（書）。」",
   "zh_bytes": 53,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 927,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "lord,brit,old,book",
   "zh": "不列顛王,舊,書",
   "zh_bytes": 14,
   "note": "keyword 群組"
  },
  {
   "offset": 946,
   "len": 87,
   "en": "\"Lord British treasures antiques. There is one book for which he hath offered a reward:",
   "zh": "「不列顛王珍視古物。有一本書他願以重金懸賞：",
   "zh_bytes": 44,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1036,
   "len": 22,
   "en": "\"'The Wizard of @Oz.'\"",
   "zh": "「『@Oz（奧茲）巫師』。」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": "@Oz → @奧茲；@wiza 觸發後續說明（書名）"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1064,
   "len": 7,
   "en": "wiza,oz",
   "zh": "巫,奧茲",
   "zh_bytes": 7,
   "note": "keyword 群組緊"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1072,
   "len": 37,
   "en": "\"By Master L. Frank Baum, I believe.\"",
   "zh": "「想是 L·法蘭克·鮑姆 所著。」",
   "zh_bytes": 31,
   "note": "L. Frank Baum → 法蘭克·鮑姆（glossary）"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1112,
   "len": 74,
   "en": "\"It concerns a girl adventurer, a strange land, and a clever @balloonist.\"",
   "zh": "「書中講一少女冒險者、奇境，以及一名聰穎的@balloonist（氣球）師。」",
   "zh_bytes": 53,
   "note": "@balloonist → @氣球師"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1192,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "ball",
   "zh": "氣球",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "@balloon keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1197,
   "len": 57,
   "en": "\"Are they not made of @silk, in the form of a great bag?\"",
   "zh": "「莫非以@silk（絲）製成，狀如大袋？」",
   "zh_bytes": 31,
   "note": "@silk → @絲綢"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1260,
   "len": 8,
   "en": "silk,bag",
   "zh": "絲,袋",
   "zh_bytes": 5,
   "note": "keyword 群組"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1269,
   "len": 53,
   "en": "\"'Tis a wondrous strong stuff, silk, and very light.\"",
   "zh": "「絲乃奇強之物，輕巧無比。」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1325,
   "len": 55,
   "en": "\"I regret that I am not skillful enough to weave silk.\"",
   "zh": "「可惜我手藝未足以織絲。」",
   "zh_bytes": 26,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1383,
   "len": 61,
   "en": "\"In New Magincia, however, lives the silk-weaver @Charlotte.\"",
   "zh": "「然而新馬精西亞有一織絲師@Charlotte（夏綠）蒂居於彼處。」",
   "zh_bytes": 45,
   "note": "@Charlotte → @夏綠蒂；New Magincia → 新馬精西亞"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1450,
   "len": 4,
   "en": "char",
   "zh": "夏綠",
   "zh_bytes": 4,
   "note": "@Charlotte keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1455,
   "len": 54,
   "en": "\"She is the only person I know of who can weave silk.\"",
   "zh": "「她是我所知唯一能織絲之人。」",
   "zh_bytes": 30,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1515,
   "len": 3,
   "en": "bye",
   "zh": "別",
   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "@bye keyword"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1519,
   "len": 37,
   "en": "\"May our paths cross again some day.\"",
   "zh": "「願日後我等再會。」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1561,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "\"That I cannot help thee with.\"",
   "zh": "「此事我無能為力。」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": "預設不解回應"
  },
  {
