   "zh_bytes": 2,
   "note": "yes/no token"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1918,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "\"You look pretty full to me.\"",
   "zh": "「汝看來已滿載。」",
   "zh_bytes": 18,
   "note": "背包滿"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2016,
   "len": 61,
   "en": "\"Excellent!\" After accepting $Y's gold, $N hands over the $0.",
   "zh": "「妙！」收下$Y的金錢後，$N將$0交予。",
   "zh_bytes": 36,
   "note": "成交描述"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2093,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"You haven't the money.\"",
   "zh": "「汝身上無此金錢。」",
   "zh_bytes": 20,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2138,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"That is fine $0.\"",
   "zh": "「此乃上好$0。」",
   "zh_bytes": 16,
   "note": "保留 $0"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2164,
   "len": 26,
   "en": "\"You'll find none better.\"",
   "zh": "「再無更好者。」",
   "zh_bytes": 16,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2324,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Sorry, none of you has anything I need.\"",
   "zh": "「抱歉，汝等無我所需之物。」",
   "zh_bytes": 28,
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2426,
